@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
    ViewBag.Title = "Connectors & Accessories – Drip Smart USA";
    ViewBag.MetaDescription = "DripSmart fittings, barbed connectors, end caps, goof plugs, and accessories for drip tape and dripline systems.";
}

<section class="page-hero" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #181F4E 0%, #1e2d6e 100%);">
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
        <div class="page-hero-text">
            <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/products">Products</a> / <span>Connectors & Accessories</span></nav>
            <h1>Connectors, Fittings & Accessories</h1>
            <p>Every professional drip system depends on the small parts working perfectly. DripSmart fittings and accessories are engineered to the same tolerances as our emitters — no weak links.</p>
            <a href="/find-a-dealer" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:24px;">Find a Local Dealer</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Categories -->
<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header centered">
            <span class="section-eyebrow">Product Categories</span>
            <h2>Everything to Complete the System</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="three-col-grid" style="margin-top:40px;">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🔗</div>
                <h3>Barbed Fittings</h3>
                <p>Couplings, elbows, tees, and crosses for 1/2", 5/8", 3/4", and 1" poly tubing and drip tape. Compression-barb design requires no tools — push-and-lock installation.</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <li>Straight couplings, 90° and 45° elbows</li>
                    <li>Equal and reducing tees</li>
                    <li>Figure-9 and barbed crosses</li>
                    <li>Sold in bags of 10, 25, and 100</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🔒</div>
                <h3>Lock Rings & Compression Fittings</h3>
                <p>Positive-lock fittings for high-pressure mainline connections and permanent installations. Resists blow-off under surge pressure — required for 3/4"+ mainline use.</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <li>Sizes: 3/4", 1", 1-1/4", 1-1/2", 2"</li>
                    <li>Rated to 100 PSI working pressure</li>
                    <li>NSF-listed materials</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🔴</div>
                <h3>End Caps & Goof Plugs</h3>
                <p>End caps seal lateral ends and flush valves. Goof plugs fill unwanted punch holes — essential for field repairs when emitters are moved or accidentally punched.</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <li>Drip tape end caps (fold & lock)</li>
                    <li>1/2" and 3/4" poly end caps</li>
                    <li>Goof plugs: 1/4" and 17mm barb sizes</li>
                    <li>Bulk bags of 50 and 100</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">⬆️</div>
                <h3>Risers & Takeoffs</h3>
                <p>Punch takeoffs, saddle clamps, and riser assemblies for connecting sub-mains to laterals. Available for PVC, poly, and layflat supply lines in common sizes.</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <li>Barbed punch takeoffs (1/2" and 3/4")</li>
                    <li>Saddle clamps for PVC sub-mains</li>
                    <li>Riser assemblies 6"–24"</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🏷️</div>
                <h3>Tape Connectors</h3>
                <p>Start connectors, inline connectors, and figure-9 ends specifically designed for drip tape. Maintain a water-tight seal even under repeated seasonal installation and removal.</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <li>Compatible with all DripSmart tape sizes</li>
                    <li>Swivel start connectors available</li>
                    <li>Lock-ring versions for high flow</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-icon">🛠️</div>
                <h3>Tools & Install Equipment</h3>
                <p>Punch tools, tubing cutters, and tape rollers that make installation faster and cleaner. The right tool prevents the most common installation mistakes.</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:12px;">
                    <li>1/4" and 17mm punch tools</li>
                    <li>Poly tubing cutter (ratchet type)</li>
                    <li>Drip tape retrieval reels</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section" style="background:var(--midnight); color:white;">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 style="color:white;">Stocked at Your Local DripSmart Dealer</h2>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); max-width:520px; margin:16px auto 0;">Fittings, end caps, goof plugs, and tools are stocked locally so you can get what you need when you need it — not waiting on a shipment.</p>
        <a href="/find-a-dealer" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:28px; display:inline-block;">Find a Dealer Near You</a>
    </div>
</section>
